features.displayName: Tropical Storm and Hurricane Impacted Now
features.name: Hurricane Storm Impacted Now

rule.ruleString:
function isStormNow(){
 var winterPhenomenaCode = ["BZ", "WS","LE","IS","blizzard","freezeRain","TSI", "snowSquall", "snowFall","winterStorm"]

 return (context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert !== null) && 
  (context.weatherSummary.nearestSnowAccumulation !== null) && 
  (winterPhenomenaCode.indexOf(context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert.phenomenaCode) !== -1) &&
  (context.weatherSummary.nearestWinterStormAlert.significanceCode == "W") && 
  context.weatherSummary.nearestSnowAccumulation.snowRange !== null &&
  context.weatherSummary.nearestSnowAccumulation.snowRange !== "0"	
 
}

isStormNow()
